Static Methods

composeLeft<A, B>(e1 : Either<A, B>, e2 : Either<A, B>, ac : A -> A -> A, bc : B -> B -> B) : Either<A, B>

Composes two Eithers together. In case of conflicts, "failure" (left) always wins.

composeRight<A, B>(e1 : Either<A, B>, e2 : Either<A, B>, ac : A -> A -> A, bc : B -> B -> B) : Either<A, B>

Composes two Eithers together. In case of conflicts, "success" (right) always wins.
